title: Eighth Continent T1 Edgar Poe (Agarthy & Sosich)cbr
description:
Baltimore,USA,thursday,september 27,1849:The trace of Edgar Poe is lost in the moment he disembarked from the ferry from Richmond.He reappears six days later.
Victim of a conspiracy,Edgar meanwhile lived his worst nightmare...and his last love.His supernatural enemies and others are constantly pursuing him.
His crime:wanting to reveal a secret to the world that never should be in any event...
